    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 40-43.</p><p>Avenger of the Wild</p><p>Also at 21st level, your attunement to the wild allows you to call upon natural disasters. As an action, you can expend a Wild Shape use to cast one of the following spells once per day without expending a spell slot: Earthquake, Incendiary Cloud, or Sunburst. Once you use this feature to cast one of these spells, you cannot use it to cast the same spell again until you finish a long rest.</p><p>LP Cost. You can use this feature at the end of another creature’s turn by expending 1 Legendary Point.</p></div>",
